                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="16516404" author="jrwest" created="Mon, 18 Jun 2018 21:59:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Made&#160;the cache invalidation run&#160;after the files are added to the tracker. This is similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/blob/trunk/src/java/org/apache/cassandra/db/streaming/CassandraStreamReceiver.java#L207-L210&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;streaming&lt;/a&gt;. There is still a race condition but the worst case is only invalidation of a cached copy of the newly added data.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Branch:&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/jrwest/cassandra/commits/14529-trunk&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/jrwest/cassandra/commits/14529-trunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 Tests:&#160;&lt;a href=&quot;https://circleci.com/gh/jrwest/cassandra/tree/14529-trunk&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://circleci.com/gh/jrwest/cassandra/tree/14529-trunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16518118" author="jasobrown" created="Wed, 20 Jun 2018 13:13:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed as sha &lt;tt&gt;73e70340a173b8ff56665cddb70756e83f7d37b0&lt;/tt&gt;. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
